      ],
      "source": "https://lyonsfallsny.gov/"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "In 1794 French refugees founded High Falls, now Lyons Falls, where Moose and Black rivers crash over seventy‑foot rocks.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
