      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lyons_Falls%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "A history club formed in May 2005 evolved into the Lyons Falls History Association, a non‑profit chartered by the state.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
